imdb.plot outline: The travel adventure TV show Outside Explorer travels to Cathedral Gorge State Park in Nevada. Adventurers of all ages love exploring the slot canyons via a network of walking trails which provide great views of the park, which happens to be a photographers dream! If you are looking for travel destination inspiration, we are here to help! Outside Explorer airs on Root Sports Sunday mornings at 8:30 Find our fan page on Facebook: Outside Explorer
imdb.title: Outside Explorer: Cathedral Gorge State Park
